                            <comment id="389341" author="adilger" created="Mon, 16 Oct 2023 03:20:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue has already been fixed in master by limiting the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;C &amp;#45;1&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; stripe count to LOV_MAX_STRIPE_COUNT by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/50250&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/50250&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16623&quot; title=&quot;lod_statfs_and_check() does not skip unusable OSTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16623&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16623&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lod: handle object allocation consistently&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; that landed as commit v2_15_56-1-gced540165e.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
